    <title>Real Transparency in Airfares Act of 2016</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Real Transparency in Airfares Act of 2016</b></p> <p> This bill sets at $55,000, or $2,500 for an individual or small business, the maximum civil penalty assessed on a person for an unfair or deceptive practice relating to unfair methods of competition in air transportation, the sale of air transportation, or specified regulations relating to price advertising and opt-out requirements. </p>]]></text>
